social_posts.post_text: If you’re celebrating the Christmas season in Prague this is the perfect single day itinerary 🙏🏽 luckily we were staying at the @fsprague which was a 5 minute walk from basically everything, but regardless this itinerary is very doable in one day!

social_posts.post_text: @fstentrinity was a destination in its own right. The whole place was amazing but watching movies by the fireplace around Christmas and feeling that level of comfort will be one of my favorite new memories 🙏🏽
Beautiful Christmas decorations, perfect locations and top tier service

Paris is a beautiful but busy city, and I’ve always had a hard time finding a place that had a relaxing vibe, but was perfectly in the middle of everything and @mo_paris did it better than I could have imagined 🙏🏽
Loved every minute of Prague but take our advice and make the most of the twilight hours 🙏🏽
Lived so close my whole life and still finding more here 🙏🏽

5 Things to do in Abu Dhabi: 

1. Camel Trekking at @anantaraqasralsarab (one of the many activities to do in the resort, including sandboarding, desert drives, archery, etc)

2. Enjoy a romantic private dinner for two at @anantaraqasralsarab 

3. Head over to the Wahat Al Karama war memorial and monument.

4. Visit the majestic Sheikh Zayed Grand Mosque. 

5. A trip to Abu Dhabi isn’t complete without a visit to the historic @emiratespalace . Enjoy a day lounging in one of their beach cabanas with plenty of water activities including paddle boarding, kayaking, jet skis, etc).

Staycations at the @langhamnyc hit different! Also who else can say they are lucky enough to get proposed to two years in a row from the same man?! This one of course was a planned proposal for a shoot but still enjoyed this beautiful setup organized by @fleurish_nyc

Airbnb is @ecosixbali and it really was one of the most unique places I’m assuming I’ll ever stay
